Names and Attributes	How the Real becomes knowable
Levels of Being	Degrees through which manifestation unfolds
Cosmos	The macrocosmic display of divine names
Human	The microcosmic condensation of the cosmos
Perfect Human	The complete mirror and total form
Muhammadan Reality	The supreme archetype of human completion
