1. Source identity

Primary source: ʿAbd al-Raḥmān Jāmī, Lawāʾiḥ, usually translated as Flashes of Light or A Treatise on Sufism.

Best public-access base: E. H. Whinfield and Mīrzā Muḥammad Qazvīnī’s 1906 edition/translation is available on Internet Archive.

